                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>In a conversation held in London March 11, Ambassador Jessup and representatives
                    of the British Foreign Office in part discussed attitudes of other Asian nations
                    towards a Japanese peace treaty and the economic revival of Japan. For a record
                    of the conversation, see <ref target="#pg_46">page 46</ref>.</p>
            </div>
